Database:

FR1.1 System will store user, customer, and books in a database(M)

Report:

FR2.1 Allow user to view product sale reports based on past and current data(S)

FR2.2 Allow user to view a forecasted report based on past demand data(S)

Customization:

FR3.1 Allows user to set an inventory threshold that alerts user user of low stock(M)

FR3.2 Allows user to categorize database by adding genre, author, keyword, and ISBN(M)

FR3.3 Allows user to add, change, delete alert messages for customers (C)
